creator: gkukreja@cisco.com
text:
Hi I am implementing this version .20.4 in our project . Problem I am facing 
is : If we run the example of FOP  using servlet with fo-> PDF then it shows 
the output in IE5.5 but when we try to do xml/xsl-> pdf like the glossary 
example it doesn't work. Ne Help .

TIA
Girish

creator: oleg@tkachenko.com
text:
It's well-known IE5.5 bug, see fop-user list archive for details. Upgrade to IE6
(not sure) or add dummy parameter to the end of url, e.g
http://your.server.../FopServlet?xml=...&xsl=...&dummy=.pdf
batch transition to closed remaining pre-FOP1.0 resolved bugs
